/-- The class number of a principal ideal domain is `1`. -/
theorem card_class_group_eq_one [is_principal_ideal_ring R] : fintype.card (class_group R) = 1 :=
  by
  rw [fintype.card_eq_one_iff]
  use 1
  refine' class_group.induction (fraction_ring R) fun I => _
  exact class_group.mk_eq_one_iff.mpr (I : fractional_ideal (non_zero_divisors R) (fraction_ring R)).is_principal
